  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The station masters are asking for time to increase the train fares",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kasun Chamara, Secretary of the Railway Station Master's Association, informed the Railway General Manager in writing today (21) afternoon that the Executive Committee of the Sri Lanka Railway Station Master's Association has decided not to implement the railway fare revision from midnight tomorrow (22).",
        "The letter has further informed that there is not enough time to inform the passengers about the fare revision, less than a day is not enough for the accounting work and related work in the railway stations and this situation is causing inconvenience to the station masters and passengers."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
